# Install

## Install packages and active them
./scripts/build.sh --install

## Check Active gettext
phpinfo(): GetText Support enabled
Status page

## Install Libraries and Dependencies
./scripts/upgrade.sh


# Translations (Implementing more languages)
### Edit ./locale/ files with a PO file editor:
https://poedit.net/
https://localise.biz/free/poedit


# Other Scripts

## Generate Documentation
./scripts/gen_doc.sh

## Check PHP files syntax
./scripts/check_php.sh

## Fix permissions
./scripts/do_chmod.sh

